<text name="text_PLAYER_SHIP_TRASH_MINER_name">Garbage Compactor</text>
<text name="text_PLAYER_SHIP_TRASH_MINER_desc">An old Kestrel class ship intended for light asteroid mining and garbage removal. Refitted for combat by the Sergal Engineer Cheese, who was joined by the Protogen TRACKER and Primagen RAPTOR. A malfunction in the clonebay's DNA Backup created Lancer.</text>
<text name="ship_PLAYER_SHIP_TRASH_MINER_unlock">Side with Tracker in the conflict with the Trash Compactor</text>

