<text name="text_PLAYER_SHIP_TRASH_MINER_B_desc">Ice Ice Ion. Lancer had way too much fun remaking the Garbage Compactor to suit his weird needs, and has made the ultimate boarding ship - as long as you ignore the tiny size of the teleporter. Ice ice ion.</text>
